        "content": "<h1 align=\"center\">martinbaud</h1>\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <b>Software craftsman</b> · Paris<br>\n  <sub>Building <a href=\"https://aeryflux.com\">AeryFlux</a> — explore the world through music, news, and data on an interactive 3D globe.</sub>\n</p>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n\n<a href=\"https://aeryflux.com\">\n  <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/aeryflux.com-Visit-3b82f6?style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"aeryflux.com\">\n</a>\n\n<br><br>\n\n<a href=\"https://github.com/aeryflux\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/GitHub-aeryflux-181717?style=flat-square&logo=github\" alt=\"GitHub\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/org/aeryflux\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/npm-@aeryflux-cb3837?style=flat-square&logo=npm\" alt=\"npm\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://atlas.aeryflux.com\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Atlas-live-10b981?style=flat-square\" alt=\"Atlas\"></a>\n\n</div>\n\n---\n\n"
